iwts_performer:1194 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Al Simmons";
  schema:description """He's a musician! He’s an inventor! He's a nut! His astounding gadgets and preposterous songs have entertained audiences for over 55 years. Multi-Award winner Al Simmons is a creative genius whose highly original performances of profound wackiness and of off-the-wall inventions have taken the arts of Music and Comedy to unparalleled heights of hilarity. Young or old, you cannot fail to appreciate this man’s frenetic stage antics and mind-boggling lovableness.   

