  schema:name "Matt Baker";
  schema:description "Matt Baker is a comedian and odd-skill specialist who holds three Guinness World Records and has appeared on America’s Got Talent, The Late Late Show with James Corden, and ESPN. His high-energy, family-friendly show blends audience participation, hilarious stories, and jaw-dropping stunts. A full-time pro for over 24 years, Matt has performed in 22 countries and is a top variety act on Disney Cruise Line, entertaining audiences ages 7 to 97.";
