iwts_performer:1339 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Lucas Miller";
  schema:description """Known nationwide as the \"singing zoologist,\" Lucas Miller has introduced millions to the wonders of nature with his multimedia science presentations. Blending smart songwriting, zany humor, and creative video, Miller keeps audiences entranced while they learn about metamorphosis, ocean food chains, adaptations, and other curriculum-based science lessons.

Author of five children's books and host of a vibrant YouTube channel, Lucas has been setting a new standard for educational programs for over 30 years.""";
