  schema:name "Dan Kamin";
  schema:description "DAN KAMIN is an internationally renowned movement artist, magician, comedy choreographer and theatrical prankster.  On film, he created the physical comedy sequences for CHAPLIN and BENNY & JOON, And trained Robert Downey, Jr. and Johnny Depp for their acclaimed starring performances.  He also played the wooden Indian that came to life in the cult classic CREEPSHOW 2, and created the Martian girl’s weird movement for Tim Burton’s horror spoof MARS ATTACKS!";
