iwts_performer:1636 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Royal Wood";
  schema:description "Royal Wood is a Saskatoon based singer songwriter known for his warm baritone, timeless melodies, and deeply human storytelling. Since being named iTunes Songwriter of the Year, Royal has continued to evolve and refine his craft, building on a career that includes two Top 30 albums, multiple JUNO nominations, five Canadian Folk Music Award nods and a Number 1 added song at Hot AC radio. His previous album What Tomorrow Brings was up for consideration for Best Folk Album at the 2024 Grammy Awards.";
