iwts_performer:1814 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Letters Aloud";
  schema:description """Real letters, by real people, read by professional actors. 

Since 2014, we have traveled all over the country sharing intimate letters written by individuals who have left their mark on history. With a power to evoke both laughter and deep emotion, these letters serve as a testament to humanity's extraordinary ability to unearth hope, purpose, and happiness amidst life's challenges.

With live musical accompaniment and a dynamic slideshow, a Letters Aloud evening is guaranteed to inspire!""";
