iwts_performer:2123 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Sylvia Chave";
  schema:description """Sylvia Chave: Queen of the Swing-Set-Scene

Sylvia Chave doesn’t just perform—she captivates, wrapping kids in music, laughter, and imagination. With witty lyrics and toe-tapping tunes, she sings about childhood joys and hiccups, from blankie blues to why moms know everything. On stage, she’s pure magic—transforming from a princess to a pirate in seconds. With vibrant costumes, interactive fun, and boundless energy, Sylvia keeps kids singing, dancing, and giggling long after the show ends.""";
