iwts_performer:3229 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Laila Biali";
  schema:description "Multi award-winning and 2026 GRAMMY nominated vocalist, pianist and CBC broadcaster Laila Biali has headlined venues across 5 continents from New York's Carnegie Hall to Beijing's National PAC, and supported international icon Sting. With a signature sound that transcends genre, Laila \"masterfully mixes jazz and pop, bringing virtuosity and unpredictability to songs that are concise and catchy\" (Washington Post). Her dynamic live concerts feature reimagined classics, heartfelt originals and storytelling, garnering rave reviews around the globe.";
