iwts_performer:4101 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Yuki The Juggler";
  schema:description """Award-winning Japanese Canadian juggler & circus artist Yuki has captivated audiences worldwide since 2007. From street shows in Europe to honing his craft in Africa, he blends physical comedy with technical brilliance. 
Yuki is also a practitioner of Edo Daikagura, a 400-year-old Japanese art form combining object balancing, umbrella ball spinning, and storytelling. Using handcrafted Japanese props, Yuki modernizes the art while preserving its cultural essence, creating an experience that is both mesmerizing and engaging.""";
  schema:url <http://www.yukithejuggler.com>;
