  schema:name "Geneviève Racette";
  schema:description "Geneviève Racette is a bilingual folk-pop-Americana artist from Quebec whose ethereal vocals and heartfelt songwriting captivate audiences worldwide. Winner of the 2020 Canadian Folk Music Award for Emerging Artist, she’s earned acclaim from Rolling Stone, CBC, and more. Her latest album, Golden (2024), debuted at #3 on the Folk Alliance International charts, showcasing her most personal and powerful songs yet.";
