  schema:name "Buzz Brass";
  schema:description "Featuring fresh musical arrangements in a unique repertoire that brilliantly blends classical music and various styles, combined with a strong stage presence that appeals to a wide audience, Buzz Brass is one of the most renowned brass quintets in Canada. Since 2002, the ensemble has presented over 2,000 concerts, reaching over 500,000 music lovers throughout North America, Europe and China. Last season, 130 concerts were presented throughout Canada. A record-breaking season and a great success for this “top-notch brass quintet” (CBC Music).";
