  schema:description "Chiara Izzi is an award-winning jazz singer and composer from Italy, based in NYC since 2014. A Montreux Jazz Festival winner, she blends Italian music with jazz, Mediterranean, and pop influences, singing in four languages. Praised for her soulful voice and musical depth, her latest albums Live in Bremen and Across the Sea showcase her storytelling and cross-cultural artistry, described as “a force of nature” and “a talent to be heard, admired, and anticipated.";
