  schema:name "Ty Koch";
  schema:description """Emerging singer/songwriter Ty Koch is the type of artist who can seamlessly blend genres; crooner, blues, musical theatre, classical, and every vintage rock song you can think of. His repertoire includes over 50 covers, and a dozen originals.

