iwts_performer:7539 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Donné Roberts";
  schema:description """Singer-songwriter and guitarist. 2 times JUNO Award Winner, 4 times JUNO Nominee. Donne's album “OYA” was nominated for JUNO Award in 2022. In May 2024 Donné won the 1st Place at the International Songwriting Competition in the USA. With over 14,000 entries from over 120 countries, this award confirms Donné’s impressive creativity and songwriting talent.”
Donné known for his consistently delivering a high quality and high energy live performances and for his impressive compositions. Donné Roberts is one of the top world music band in Toronto.""";
