iwts_performer:7826 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "O Come All Ye Soulful Feat. Dawn Pemberton & Jodi Proznick";
  schema:description """Join two award winning powerhouses – vocalist, Dawn Pemberton and bassist/bandleader, Jodi Proznick and an all-star band as they bring a joyful and soulful bounce to your favorite holiday classics.

The music includes holiday gems made famous by Ray Charles, Stevie Wonder, Ella Fitzgerald, John Legend, Donny Hathaway, Otis Redding, Vince Guaraldi, and more! 

Join Western Canadian Music Award winners and Juno Nominee Dawn Pemberton (vocals), Jodi Proznick (bass), and the band for a soulful holiday celebration.""";
