  schema:description "Rachel DeShon was the winner of Marvin Hamlisch’s Search for a Star competition. At home with symphonies, opera houses, theatre productions and even circus tents, she's proven to be a versatile performer and strives to use her voice in exciting and dynamic ways. Kozmo Sammartino is a graduate of St. Clair College’s Music Theatre Performance program and received his Bachelors degree from Atlantic Technological University in Silgo, Ireland. He's passionate about classical music and creating positive social change through music and storytelling.";
