iwts_performer:8565 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "KeAloha";
  schema:description """KeAloha's music carries essences of their Hawaiian, Tahitian and Lheidli T'enneh Indigeneity; woven with Brown & Black artists and music lineages who have importantly mentored KeAloha’s voice. Keali’i Reichel meets Jhene Aiko, Thundercat meets Olivia Rodrigo. \"Dynamic, multi-pronged musical paradise. Grounded, Elevated, oceanic, bars, all of it\" (Music Waste Festival). ?KeAloha weaves soundscapes of Indigi-Soul wonder, beaming and shapeshifting as a vocalist, drummer, and dancer.  

They perform with a trio-quartet.""";
