iwts_performer:8633 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Eric Paetkau";
  schema:description """Two-time JUNO-nominated folksinger-songwriter Eric Paetkau captivates audiences with beautiful melodies and heartfelt storytelling, radiating pure joy throughout his performances. As he weaves together original songs and old favourites, he creates a musical experience that resonates with listeners of all ages. 

Eric was the conductor of the Saskatoon Symphony Orchestra and the group of 27 Chamber Orchestra. He’s appeared in concert halls worldwide, including Carnegie Hall and Amsterdam’s Concertgebouw as a guest conductor and violist.""";
