  schema:description "Hot on the heels of her energetic single ‘You Can Find Me,’ Julia Vos is on the rise in the country music scene, with 3 nominations at the Country Music Alberta awards and a finalist spot in the 2023 Boots and Hearts Emerging Artist Showcase. Her blend of Bluegrass roots and modern country hooks has earned her spots at major festivals like Big Valley Jamboree and Calgary Stampede. Her latest single, \"Somebody,\" hit 20K  streams in two weeks, and her TikTok has over a million views. Julia’s new single \"I Only Kiss Cowboys\" drops this spring.";
