iwts_performer:8917 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Aliya Kanani";
  schema:description """Aliya, an award-winning comedian, Canadian academy award-nominated actress and writer, captivates audiences globally with her vibrant personality and sharp wit. 

Her one-woman show, ‘Where You FROM, From?’ celebrated for its humour and deep engagement with themes of identity and belonging, has won accolades at several festivals. Aliya disarms audiences with her playful mischief, tackling complex topics like race, gender, and social labels with humour, sharing personal stories from her life as a nomad while debunking assumptions.""";
