  schema:name "Radhika Baskar";
  schema:description """Radhika Baskar, an accomplished Veena player, has a rich knowledge of traditional South Indian Carnatic Music with skills in improvisation. Beyond Indian classical, Radhika  pushes her boundaries and showcases her versatility in fusion music, fronting a dynamic and increasingly popular ensemble. Radhika's Veena mastery blends traditional Carnatic roots with contemporary flair and fusion sensibilities. 
 
