  schema:name "Real Sweat Performance Group";
  schema:description "Real Sweat Performance Group is a wildly sexy, bi-cross-racial, queer, seductively provocative, overly energetic, underappreciated (underage) ad hoc performance collective co-created by dance artist Tia Ashley Kushniruk ? ?? and theatre creator Philip Jonah Logan Geller. The collaborative relationship was forged in the fires of a bouffon workshop in 2023 the duo has been sweating ever since. Blurring the lines of traditional performance we tackle themes of racial oppression, white supremacy, collective existential angst and coffee enemas.";
