  schema:name "Allan Carr";
  schema:description "Janie Rothfield (fiddle/banjo/vocals) and Allan Carr (guitar/mandola/vocals) play a unique blend of Scottish and American songs and tunes, many original, on fiddle, guitar, mandola, and clawhammer banjo! Their ability to merge these styles comes from years of living, touring and recording in the UK, Europe and USA, playing concerts, clubs and festivals,etc.";
