iwts_performer:9346 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Mandy Faye";
  schema:description "Mandy Faye (Mandy Morris) (they/them), since 2017, has been spreading joy through song and encourages everyone to embrace inclusivity and  creativity through music. Best described as Sesame Street meets Diana Krall, their high-energy stage presence and thoughtful lyrics have won the hearts of all who have come to their shows and workshops. Mandy has won the YYC Music Award in 2021 and has been nominated for the WCMA.  Mandy is releasing their third album in 2025 and they have toured  in Alberta, BC, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Nova Scotia and NWT.";
