iwts_performer:9380 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Sidewalk Cellist - Clara Shandler";
  schema:description """Vancouver’s Clara Shandler performs under the moniker Sidewalk Cellist. She's performed on three continents, her music has been featured in films and has been performed by small ensembles and orchestras, she's collaborated with dancers, poets and theatre productions to create memorable experiences, and has released her fourth full-length album in September 2024.

Sounds Like Joni Mitchell meets Nirvana meets Arvo Pärt.


Clara identifies as bi-sexual, pansexual, queer, and as an advocate for human rights, peace and environmental protection.""";
