  schema:description """Affair of Honor is a Jessie nominated fight and movement based theater company, focused on continuous training in the art of performance combat, ensemble building and multiple mediums of physical theatre. Affair of Honor is committed to creating visually stunning fight and movement based productions as well as providing a platform for emerging artists, showcasing our diverse BIPOC & LGBTQIA+ communities and cultivating stories with women at the forefront.
