  schema:name "St. Cecilia";
  schema:description "All-female tribute band to ‘Women in Music’ St. Cecilia, covering modern and classic tunes in the pop/rock/country genre sung and/or written by Women. Named after the patroness of Music and Musicians, Guitarist Carla Olive, Bassist Lindsay Ward and Drummer Amber Banman take the listener on a journey through the decades of the female contribution to the world of music.";
