  schema:name "Firebird";
  schema:description "Firebird is made up of three accomplished singer-songwriters, living and working on traditional Quw'utsun lands on Vancouver Island, leaning heavily into gorgeous three part harmonies and catchy heartfelt songs. With guitar, piano, accordion, and bouzouki they meld irish, bluegrass and pop to create a fusion folk that is full of fire and redemption.";
