iwts_performer:9405 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "CocoLarosa";
  schema:description """Hailing from Surrey BC, CocoLarosa is a folk singer/songwriter specializing in
rhythmically bombastic and lyrically driven storytelling.

In the summer of 2024 he won the Fraser Valley Music ‘People’s Choice Award’
and was also nominated for the FVMA ‘Folk/Roots Artist of the Year.’

Known for his passionate performances and high caliber lyricism, his authentic
narratives stir up emotion and resonate with people in all walks of life.""";
