iwts_performer:9409 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "JACE CARRILLO";
  schema:description """JACE Carrillo is a Venezuelan Canadian force redefining borders with his vibrant fusion of Spanish vocals and Contemporary Pop, R&B, and urban sounds. Influenced by icons like Justin Bieber, Bruno Mars, Luis Fonsi, JACE has built a sound that is as global as it is personal.

Recent highlights include a tour across Florida, festival Fuego Fuego, international and national showcases, Canada’s Top 100 Shazam Charts, features in MTV, Billboard, CBC, Televisa MX, and JUNO Fest 2026. JACE plans to release his 3rd studio album in 2026.""";
