  schema:name "Jayne Walling";
  schema:description "Jayne is an internationally recognized theatre artist and professionally trained clown who has worked all over the world, creating new exciting plays for audiences of all ages with her strong visual and comedic style. Her shows are engaging and playful, incorporating live music and drawing from her clown and mask training in Paris, France. She loves to collaborate with artists of diverse artistic and cultural backgrounds to create shows which explore social themes for young audiences in innovative and exciting new ways.";
