iwts_performer:9419 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Julia VanderVeen";
  schema:description """Julia VanderVeen is an award-winning actor and clown based in NYC.  She has trained extensively in Clown and Bouffon, and apprenticed under head of physical theatre at Yale University, Christopher Bayes. Julia's solo show \"My Grandmother's Eyepatch,\" received rave ***** reviews last year at the Edinburgh Fringe Festival, and was featured in the NY Times!

Julia is also developing a solo show called \"Dentata\" about female ferocity and pleasure, and a female Bouffon show entitled \"Stand Back and Stand By\" about the January 6th insurrection.""";
