  schema:name "Secondhand Dreamcar";
  schema:description "Secondhand Dreamcar is a 9-piece soul, roots and contemporary blues band based in amiskwacîwâskahikan (Edmonton) on Treaty 6 territory.  This group of Alberta heavies is crafting a distinct, funky, and lyrically driven sound that journalist and programmer Peter North has deemed the most exciting thing to come out of Edmonton since k.d. lang and The Reclines.";
