  schema:name "Tracie Skeet-Brook";
  schema:description "Tracie Skeet-Brook is a passionate, multifaceted artist with a classical and world music background. She creates unique, high standard music performances in Celtic, Christmas,  Musical Theatre, Folk, Classical, Opera, Jazz, Blues vocal repertoire while playing numerous instruments including the piano, penny whistles, lap harp, glockenspiel, Merlin and more. She also produces her own background music which can include orchestral productions. Her versatile, creative and emotional performances connect with audiences where you will want more.";
