  schema:name "The Sound Of Eddy";
  schema:description "Montreal duo The Sound Of Eddy is the fruit of a collaboration between singer Abigail Galwey and bassist Danny Trudeau. The artistic whirlwind triggered by the collision of these two minds is at the core of their sonic identity. Inspired by trip-hop, psychedelic soul and punk, as well as literature and theater, The Sound Of Eddy absorbs these influences to create something original and unique.";
