  schema:name "Rome IX";
  schema:description "Rome IX is a Canadian Indie-Soul musician whose artistry spans music, acting, and filmmaking. Based in Calgary, Rome draws inspiration from personal and observed experiences, ever a student of the human condition. A two-time YYC Music Awards nominee, his artistry is defined by a passion for deep lyrics, soulful arrangements, and storytelling influenced by artists like Jason Mraz, Miguel, and Stevie Wonder.";
