iwts_performer:9564 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Tom Briscoe";
  schema:description "Get ready for a hilarious comedy show called \"It’s Not Mansplaining, It’s Old Mansplaining\" featuring Tom Briscoe. Tom is a well-known figure in the comedy scene, having performed at prestigious venues nationwide.  Tom shares side-splitting stories about his humorous take on navigating the male-female dynamic in a household dominated by his wife, daughters, and their assertive female Pomeranian. Critics praise Tom Briscoe’s unique brand of clean humor, and he is recognized as one of the busiest and funniest comedians of our time.";
