iwts_performer:9567 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "D'Lai";
  schema:description """Consistently headlining sold out shows around the country, D'Lai’s material and sets extend from his destitute beginnings to the experiences that have made him the man
he is today. Transparent, raw and uncut, D’Lai leaves it all on the stage. No questions, no secrets, no lies, this man is a master of his craft bringing his audiences to their feet after every show.

With over 2.4 million followers across social platforms, D’Lai has amassed a core following from his hilarious reaction videos and stand-up appearances on television.""";
