  schema:name "Love Empire";
  schema:description """Love Empire is a roots rock reggae band based in Edmonton. Established in 2024 by original members of JUNO nominated Souljah Fyah, and Isokan Africa, the mission is to chant light into the shadows, lifting up sounds of compassion and peace toward all people.

