iwts_performer:9625 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Curubandé All Star";
  schema:description """A quick search online for Indestructible Latin Orchestra this band is now back on the stage under a new name: Curubandé.  Featuring heavyweights of Latin Music such as Rodrigo Muñoz \"Papa Mambo\", Amber Epp, and Jaime Chinchilla, this band is a guarantee of authentic Afrolatin genres.  

 In July 2024, the city of Thunderbay hired the band for its main stage celebration of Canada Day.
In 2025 the band has already been selected for WInnipeg Jazz Fest, FEstival Du Voyageour, Back to 40 Fest, Frie and Water Festival and more.""";
