  schema:name "Brian Whitted";
  schema:description "Brian Whitted is a Broadway pianist, conductor, and music director whose credits include Chicago: The Musical, The Color Purple, and Bette Midler. This holiday concert is a showcase of his artistry and features a cast of powerhouse performers handpicked by Brian. Together, they deliver a dynamic and heartfelt celebration of the Christmas music that has shaped his life and career.";
