iwts_performer:9648 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Tim Nordstrom";
  schema:description """Tim is a fifth generation native Montanan who is a singer songwriter.  His notable collaborations include working with renowned artists such as George Winston, Tracy Grammer (Dave Carter), Dennis Ludiker (Asleep at the Wheel), and Lloyd Maines (father of Dixie Chicks’ Natalie Maines and producer of their Grammy-winning album “Home”).

Montana Magazine has praised his work, particularly noting his album *Under Yellowstone Skies* with a review stating, “If I had to choose one CD to represent Montana in a time capsule, this would be it.”""";
