  schema:description "Multiple CMAOntario Duo of the Year nominees and CBC Searchlight winners, Rosewood Ave blends traditional and modern country. Their single “I Won’t” hit the Top 100 Canadian Country Radio charts and landed major features on SiriusXM, Acadia Broadcasting, and Spotify editorial playlists. They’ve opened for Dallas Smith, Dean Brody, The Reklaws, and more. Their latest release, “Talk About Us,” is a high-energy duet showcasing their real-life chemistry and rising star power.";
