iwts_performer:9726 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Back of the Bus";
  schema:description """Back of the Bus is a band based in Central Saskatchewan  formed in 2003 that offers classic and contemporary folk/celtic music with Scottish, Irish and East Coast roots.
Back of the Bus plays at Ceilidhs, private functions, festivals, pubs and banquets as well as Burns’ nights and FolkFest.  
Back of the Bus was tremendously excited to be part of The National Cast for Telemiracle 44 in Regina. 
Known for solid vocals, sweetly blended harmonies, and authentic Celtic/Maritime sounds, Back of the Bus also has a well-developed sense of fun.""";
  schema:url <https://www.backofthebus.ca/>;
