  schema:name "Artie Balkwill";
  schema:description "Artie Balkwill is a songwriter with a roots and blues heart that bridges traditional and indie influences. The music he writes is deeply rooted in the soil of the prairies and nurtured by worldly travels. The rare authenticity of his soulful melodies is set to the backdrop of the adventures that have pulled him away to travel the world, and the pieces of home that have kept him coming back.";
