  schema:description "Claire Porter, A Newfoundland dynamo, Claire has taken her music to venues across Atlantic Canada, sharing her songs about love, tiramisu and detritivores.   Described as having the punch of Judy Garland and the grit of Tom Waits, Claire is an on-stage tour de force, infusing her dry wit and meticulous musicianship into every note. Claire Porter was nominated as Alternative Artist of the Year at the 2024 MusicNL Gala.";
