  schema:description "The Fog is a trio of seasoned musicians: Rick Connery on lead vocals/guitar,Gary Wilson on bass/vocals,Gwen Wilson on accordion/vocals.  Rick originates from Toronto, Gary, from Woodstock,NB and Gwen, from Halifax. All now reside in the Digby area, and have been playing in this configuration since 2022. All are experienced performers. “A Trio of the Unexpected”, with an eclectic mix of music, from a wide variety of time, type and tempo, they present both covers and originals in an unexpected mix of genres.";
  schema:url <https://www.thefognovascotia.com>;
