  schema:name "Olivia Barrett";
  schema:description "Summoning a wave of modern nostalgia, Olivia Barrett's masterful fiddle playing flows seamlessly between the old and the new, breathing life into traditional tunes through the rhythms of contemporary folk. Elegant, playful, and precise, Olivia’s music is defined by her gift for crafting new melodies from the threads of the traditions of Ireland, Scotland, and Scandinavia.";
