  schema:description """Someje is a Canadian artist of Nigerian heritage who has performed extensively as a soloist, choral singer, and collaborator with jazz ensembles, developing a distinctive vocal presence rooted in versatility, emotional depth, and a vibrant personality that shines through her performances.
