iwts_performer:9913 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Chopping Spree";
  schema:description "Chopping Spree makes every show a sight to see with their wild, intensely fun stage presence and captivating instrumental interplay. Just over a year into their musical journey, the band has hit the Vancouver music scene like a hurricane with over 1.5 organic million views on social media platforms and show after sold-out show proving anyone who doubted that people would mosh to jazz-fusion wrong. An mixture of infectious high energy hooks and jaw-dropping musicianship defies convention and makes it near impossible not to move to their music.";
