iwts_performer:9945 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Sitch";
  schema:description """Conscious themes and lyrics still exist with R&B/Pop-Soul artist Sitch, from Fayetteville, NC. As an artist, Sitch wants to make music that speaks to people, with vibrance, vulnerability, and connection. 

Sitch can soothe the vibe of your favorite coffee bar or headline your biggest festival with his energy. With a smooth voice made for R&B, a sound bold enough to be Dance Pop, and an ear built to blend harmonies, Sitch redefines what today’s music can be.""";
