  schema:name "Lauren Fox";
  schema:description "Stage and screen actress, and award winning cabaret singer, Lauren Fox's, passionate and deeply researched theatrical shows on the folk and folk-rock music of the late 60’s to early 70’s have played nightclubs, theaters and performing arts centers across the country (as well as London), all to critical acclaim. She is a MAC, Bistro and Nightlife award recipient, lauded for elevating the art form of cabaret to make it accessible to new audiences.";
