  schema:name "Alfie Zappacosta";
  schema:description """Juno® Award & American Music Award® Winning Singer-Songwriter, Alfie Zappacosta 
Alfie set his sights on music as a teen guitarist but his powerful voice and songwriting - discovered while he was in the band Surrender - launched him as a solo artist.  Hits like \"Start Again\", \"Passion\", and \"When I Fall in Love Again\" became Canadian radio staples.  He appeared on Disney's Danger Bay and contributed \"Overload\" to Dirty Dancing.  He later earned JUNO and American Music Awards recognition.""";
