  schema:name "Raga Echoes";
  schema:description "Raga Echoes is a Metro Vancouver-based live music collective presenting cinematic Indo-Western performances featuring local BC artists. The ensemble reinterprets iconic Western and global melodies using Indian classical instruments such as sitar, tabla, sarod, violin and piano. Designed for theatres and festivals, Raga Echoes creates immersive instrumental experiences that bring diverse audiences together through a shared musical language.";
