  schema:description "The Margie Gillis Dance Foundation is a Montreal-based arts organization dedicated to the creation, dissemination, and transmission of the work of choreographer and performer Margie Gillis. Internationally recognized for her deeply expressive approach to movement, the Foundation supports choreographic creation, artist mentorship, and the development of artistic and educational projects in Canada and abroad.";
