  schema:description "Bannock Dogz is the world's greatest uncle band and the only purveyors of Tsilhqot'in Honkytonk AKA Out Wessst Music! What is OUT WESSST MUSIC? It's the full spectrum of your UNCLE'S Music! TWANGIN' AND HEADBANGIN'! Bannock Dogz plays an eclectic mix of original country, classic rock, and metal through an INDIGENOUS worldview that only they have the guts to mix together!";
