iwts_performer:10036 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Shaun Jay";
  schema:description """He’s fooled Gordon Ramsay on the hit show Masterchef on FOX,
appeared on ABC, NBC, and even multiple seasons of Masters of
Illusion on the CW Network.
Shaun is constantly innovating and creating new magic to share
with his audiences and combines his love for sleight of hand, 3D
design, 3D printing, and electronics to create unique one of a kind
shows that audiences across the country remember and enjoy.
We are proud to present this unique talent and guarantee you’ll
have a great time at his show!""";
