iwts_performer:10038 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "D.O. Gibson";
  schema:description """Duane Gibson aka D.O. is a two-time Guinness World Record–setting rapper and university graduate who has inspired hundreds of thousands of youth since 2001. In 2024, D.O. was named one of the top 20 outstanding Black Canadian men by Shifter Magazine and awarded a Women of Inspiration Award for his work as an ally.

He has performed worldwide in places including Japan, England, France and South Africa in May 2024.

Gibson has freestyled with Snoop Dogg, the Raptors play his music at their games and Drake has appeared in one of his music videos.""";
