  schema:name "Jake Tkaczyk";
  schema:description """Studia Shumka is the emerging-artist ensemble of Shumka Ukrainian Dancers, showcasing the next generation of Ukrainian dance performers. These young artists bring strong technique, vibrant energy, and joy to every performance. Their performances combine athleticism and cultural storytelling for audiences of all ages.

