  schema:name "Mean Mary";
  schema:description "Mean Mary is an award-winning musician, writer, and fan favorite with over 40 million views on her YouTube videos. She grew up in music, evolving from a child prodigy busking on the streets of Nashville (“startling talent,” said The Tennessean) to a seasoned performer who has headlined more than 4,000 festivals and concerts worldwide. No Depression describes her sound as “the voice of a ragged angel combined with the banjo playing of the devil.”";
  schema:url <https://meanmary.com/>;
