  schema:description "Thiossane West African Dance Institute mission is to preserve and present traditional dance ,music and culture and to persuade its significance to future generations while promoting physical and mental wellness. The performing company of 25 yrs is steep in educational programs K-12 and collegiate curriculum along with professional programming for 30 - 90 minutes with full production, live musician and narration.";
