  schema:description "Kearstin Pfeifer is a Calgary based singer songwriter who captivates crowds with her outstanding vocals and intricately crafted songs. Born and raised in southern Saskatchewan, Kearstin began performing and songwriting from a young age. At 19, Kearstin was accepted into the songwriting and recording program at Prairie College. There, she studied her craft under the mentorship of Juno Award-Winning artist, Brian Doerksen. Kearstin often utilizes the art of storytelling through her performances and draws much of her inspiration from creation.";
  schema:url <https://www.kearstinpfeifer.com/>;
