iwts_performer:10140 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Betsy and The Bears";
  schema:description "The best way to describe the sound of Betsy and The Bears is \"Broadway Jazz meets Bossa Nova with an Americana flair\". We are a four-person band with an award-winning vocalist, a guitarist with a PH.D in Guitar Performance, a bassist with international credits, and a drummer who has shared the stage with some of the jazz staples of Indianapolis.  Our group performs a wide catalog, including original works and songs spanning from the Great American Songbook to Jobim, Dylan, and The Beatles. We also include guest artists from time to time.";
