iwts_performer:10142 a schema:Person;
  schema:name "Sydney Stephan";
  schema:description """Sydney Stephan is a New York City–based piano vocalist, and performer known for her expressive vocals, commanding musicianship, and engaging stage presence. She has performed all around the world for Disney Channel, Armed Forces Entertainment, Holland America Line, and Howl at the Moon bringing professionalism and versatility to every stage.
A New York staple- Sydney has been seen at 54 Below, and has been nominated for 8 BroadwayWorld Cabaret awards, including best vocalist.""";
