iwts_performer:10152 a schema:PerformingGroup;
  schema:name "Brass Tracks Band";
  schema:description """Brass Tracks Band is an 8 pc. band featuring an amazing 3 pc. horn section. We kick off and end our Tribute Show performing Chicago's greatest hits with all of the iconic Horn Band  hits of the 60's, 70's, 80's and beyond sandwiched in between. 
 
Our concert features Chicago along with some of the greatest Horn Bands of all time playing only their top hits. From Chicago to Multi- Platinum Award Winners Earth Wind + Fire, Blood Sweat +Tears, Tower of Power, Stevie Wonder and many more. This is the exact show BTB performs night after night!""";
