  schema:name "Ngorimba/Yegmarimba";
  schema:description "Ngorimba is a high-energy Zimbabwean marimba ensemble based in Edmonton, delivering rhythm-driven performances rooted in Southern African traditions. Blending interlocking melodies, call-and-response vocals, and audience participation, the group creates an immersive, interactive experience. Ngorimba has headlined  at Kaleidofest  Festival, KDays, Africarnival, and Heart of the City Festival, captivating diverse audiences across Alberta.";
